" {{{ tips and tricks

" {{{ extend syntax with my own 'todo' pattern

augroup vimrc_todo
    au!
    au Syntax * syn match MyTodo /\v<(todo|discuss)/ containedin=.*Comment,vimCommentTitle
augroup END
hi def link MyTodo Todo

" }}}

